content.p: Once you are here: UNMC-Guest is an open network and does not provide encryption for traffic transmitted or received by connected devices. Security for connections made using the UNMC-Guest network remains the responsibility of the user and the service is used at your own risk. Please do not enter passwords online when using this network. If you do not validate your account within the 10 minutes grace period you will be disconnected and need to re-register. telephone: +603 8924 8199 fax: +603 8924 8007 email: itservicedesk@nottingham.edu.my
